rows.label: qst650406_msg0001
rows.name:
Rex! Thanks, Rex!
And thanks, Rex's girl Blade friends!

rows.label: qst650406_msg0005
rows.name:
For a second there I thought we
were all gonna be Igna lunch...

rows.label: qst650406_msg0006
rows.name:
But when I saw this lady rushing
to save us on the Isle of Urchon,
I realized we had to keep fighting!

rows.label: qst650406_msg0008
rows.name:
So something good even came
out of the part we thought was an
unmitigated disaster, eh?

rows.label: qst650406_msg0009
rows.name:
Indeed...
It gave the lad the hope he needed.

rows.label: qst650406_msg0010
rows.name:
All right, let's get moving now.
We have to get the kids home.
